In a story published on Citizentv.co.ke website on July 28, 2021 under the headline “Probe underway after man dies at a lodging in Muranga, sex pills recovered” we inadvertently published a photo of Rurago Guest House located in Bahati, Nakuru County. We have since pulled down the said photo from all our Digital platforms and would like to apologize to the proprietor of Rurago Guest House for any damage that our story may have caused. Video Of The Day: KEMRI scientists examine safety of anti-malarial drugs in first trimester of pregnancy